You can convert the documentation into other formats.

make info  - creates info pages
make txt   - creates a plain text file
make html  - creates HTML pages
make dvi   - creates a dvi file
make pdf   - creates a PDF file
make       - makes all of the above

To read the documentation with avatarsay, use a command like this:
makeinfo --plaintext akfavatar.texinfo | avatarsay -

The documentation on the homepage may be newer than the documentation
in this package.
